ble spin switch found here shows how\nwe can not only rearrange electronic levels or lift orbital degeneracies via\nthe substrate, but even sway the effects of many-body interactions in single\nmolecules by acting on their surrounding.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Nov 2018 22:24:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-29"}
