stigate their dynamical (non-linear) stability and used\nin tandem with ray-tracing codes to obtain synthetic images of black holes\n(i.e. shadows) in astrophysically relevant situations where the light source is\nprovided by an emitting accretion disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Nov 2018 11:02:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-13"}
